{
  "title": "Purely Tender Irish Lamb Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful Irish dish featuring tender lamb and sweet glace cherries, perfect for a crowd. This Whole30-friendly stew is slow-cooked to perfection.",
  "cuisine": "Irish",
